==Other distinguished mystery stories of 2008==
Other distinguished mystery stories of 2008 honored in the volume were [[Jacob M. Appel]]'s ''Ad Valorem'' (''[[Subtropics (journal)|Subtropics]]''), [[Ron Rash]]'s ''Into the Gorge'' (''[[Southern Review]]''), Shelly Nix's ''Monkey'' (''[[Hayden's Ferry Review]]''), [[Leslie Glass (author)|Leslie Glass]]'s ''The Herald'' (''Blue Religion'') and Becky Hagenston's ''Midnight, Licorice, Shadow'' (''[[Crazyhorse (magazine)|Crazyhorse]]'').
